response.original_title: 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour | Finals in Cinema
response.overview: The wait is over. The VALORANT Champions 2025 Grand Final is here and there can only be one World Champion. After an epic VALORANT Champions Tour 2025 season, where the top teams from four International Leagues battled for one of just 16 spots to compete at Champions Paris, only two teams remain.
